$ISPO Current stock price $10 is 15% below $11.5 exercise price for the warrants with are now exercisable as of Mar 15th. In my opinion the stock price is likely to spike well above $11.5 as warrants are exercised in conjunction with A SHORT SQUEEZE.  Yes, the potential for a short squeeze is on the table.  This could happen as soon as tomorrow. Based on current share distribution I’d expect a spike to somewhere between $17-22.  Gains will be short lived as newly minted shares are sold off in conjunction with newly opened short positions. Bullish
